GET.PROPERTY:
***********************
    IN.PROPERTY.CLASS = 'OVERDUE'
    CALL APAP.AA.REDO.GET.PROPERTY.NAME(Y.ARRANGEMENT.ID,IN.PROPERTY.CLASS,R.OUT.AA.RECORD,OD.PROPERTY,OUT.ERR);*Manual R22 conversion

RETURN
